                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col width-fill">
            <div class="cell">
                <h2><span class="center icon icon-cogs icon-64"></span>Modular</h2>
                <p>
                    Don't need certain features? Don't include them. Unlike other frameworks, you can include only the components you need.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

